        {
            "title": "美元外匯衍生品溢價幾乎消失 暗示對美國國債需求減弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"604\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hGfqn0fjX48rPaFLAUkh9Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a06c82d200b1739587054ae1ec2cc787\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美元在外匯衍生品市場中的溢價正接近於零，這一跡象表明外國投資者對美國國債的需求正在減弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編的數據顯示，美元兌五種主要貨幣的加權平均三個月基差，即投資者借入一種貨幣對子而接受的溢價或折價，目前僅略低於3個基點。該基差若進一步轉為負值，將是自2020年8月以來首次。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"604\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DlsEgsHfE9U799yS7fD85g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3134b1a596cb40440f8742e0d98968e6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「外國對長期美國國債的需求減弱，可能是美元溢價消退的一個因素，」野村證券駐東京高級利率策略師Naokazu Koshimizu說道，「美國政策的不確定性可能促使投資者轉向配置非美元資產」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dollar Basis Premium Hints at Weakening Appetite for Treasuries</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E8%A1%8D%E7%94%9F%E5%93%81%E6%BA%A2%E5%83%B9%E5%B9%BE%E4%B9%8E%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E6%B8%9B%E5%BC%B1-082633009.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-25 18:00:50",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "周大福創建據悉暫停出售價值約20億美元的中國道路資產",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，香港億萬富豪鄭氏家族的基礎設施子公司暫停將價值約20億美元的中國道路資產出售的計畫，此前就此有過數月談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞社12月份報導，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:周大福;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/周大福\">周大福</a>創建有限公司正與中國國有企業越秀集團就相關交易進行磋商。但知情人士表示，由於這些資產產生的現金流穩定，周大福創建決定暫停出售。因討論未公開，知情人士要求匿名。周大福創建此前稱作新創建集團。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，周大福創建未來可能會重新考慮出售這些道路資產的計畫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周大福創建的代表不予置評。越秀集團暫未回覆尋求評論的請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Cheng Family’s CTF Said to Halt Sale of $2 Billion Road Assets</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%A6%8F%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E7%B4%8420%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2-080803540.html",
